dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Green Lake County, WI 2014
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Green Lake County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase GreenLake_Hydro_2014.gdb. The features included in the geodatabase are 'GreenLake_HydroLine_2014', and 'GreenLake_HydroPoly_2014'. This hydrography dataset originated from WI DNR 1:24K Hydro.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
